	* po/sv.po:

	1.9.12

2007-01-19  Johan Dahlin  <jdahlin@async.com.br>

	* kiwi/ui/comboentry.py (_ComboEntryPopup.set_selected_iter): 
	Try setting the full model if everything else fails.
	Based on patch by Goedson Teixeira Paixao

	Fixes #3099.

