	reviewed by: Johan Dahlin  <jdahlin@async.com.br>

	* kiwi/datatypes.py (_BaseDateTimeConverter._convert_format): 
	Use YYYY/mm/dd instead %Y/%m/%d in error messages.

	Fixes #3041.

